snippet.title: Jurnal Malam : Bestfriend - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Assalamu'alaikum wr wb

Halo sobat RiMa semuanya, sudah lama channel ini tidak meng-unggah konten selama kurang lebih hampir setengah tahun, dan Alhamdulillah sekarang sudah bisa kami tampilkan trailer Game Jurnal Malam yang kami kembangkan beberapa bulan lalu dan sempat mangkrak karena device laptop yang kami gunakan Rusak. Silakan menikmati trailer nya sembari menunggu rilis game nya heheh, terimakasih

====================================

Hello RiMa friends, it's been a long time since this channel has uploaded content for almost half a year, and thank God, now we can show the trailer for the Night Journal Game which we developed several months ago and was stopped because the laptop device we were using was damaged. Please enjoy the trailer while waiting for the game to be released heheh, thank you

Game : Jurnal Malam Bestfriend
Platform : PC, Mobile
Progress : 90%
